{"data":[{"date":"09:43 20/06","title":"S\u00e2n bay qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thay t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/san-bay-que-nha-thay-tuong-ngoi-sao-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd s\u00e2n bay Madeira, qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng anh b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi gi\u1ed1ng nguy\u00ean m\u1eabu h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Diario de Not\u00edcias Madeira, gia \u0111\u00ecnh Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi xin \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u 15/6, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ban qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd s\u00e2n bay Madeira.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u00e2n bay qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thay t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u00e2n bay qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thay t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/San-bay-que-nha-thay-tuong-ngoi-sao-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo b\u1ecb ch\u00ea v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng kh\u1eafc h\u1ecda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7n th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a anh. \u1ea2nh: AFP.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buc tuong moi duoc nhieu nguoi khen ngoi. Anh: Reuters.\" title=\"B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. \u1ea2nh: Reuters.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/35665659-10155671941017957-339-8344-5719-1529409093.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. \u1ea2nh: Reuters.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u0169. Ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a ESPN cho bi\u1ebft, danh t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ngay khi ra m\u1eaft, t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen b\u1edfi n\u00f3 l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Ronaldo ghi trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo b\u1ecb ch\u00ea l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1eafc h\u1ecda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7n th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n n\u0103m Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. Nh\u00e0 \u0111i\u00eau kh\u1eafc Emanuel Santos ban \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 &quot;Ronaldo&quot;, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh &quot;Danh d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo&quot; v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2017.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, nh\u00e0 \u0111i\u00eau kh\u1eafc Santos v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 bi\u1ec7n b\u1ea1ch cho b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo c\u0169. \u00d4ng ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf: &quot;Ngay c\u1ea3 Ch\u00faa c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m v\u1eeba l\u00f2ng h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi&quot;, v\u00e0 r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ed1ng th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Peticao Publica, v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u00edch b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169 h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eedi \u0111\u01a1n ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 cho t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Santos.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3718","checkdouble":"189005"},{"date":"09:01 20/06","title":"Sao Atletico g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cGriezmann \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u0129nh n\u00fai ti\u1ec1n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/10/costa-phat-bieu-ve-griezmann-va-hop-dong-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Diego Costa ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00e1 s\u1ed1c. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n b\u00e9o b\u1edf.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Griezmann \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1eafn do, Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m, t\u1edbi t\u1eadn n\u0103m 2023 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111i hay \u1edf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Griezmann c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Atletico r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh n\u01a1m n\u1edbp lo s\u1ee3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t anh. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia nh\u01b0 Barcelona, Real Madrid hay Man United \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 3 trong cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Costa ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Diego Costa ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/Diego-Costa-phat-bieu-ve-Griezmann-va-hop-dong-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh c\u0169ng tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/antoine-griezmann-da-cong-bo-tuong-lai-180-188510.html\" target=\"_blank\">CLB m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Griezmann m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</span> v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Atletico. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i tung m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi CLB th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Madrid kh\u00e1 ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Costa n\u1eeda \u0111\u00f9a, n\u1eeda th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Diego Costa \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t ri\u00eang. Ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f9a r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i CLB \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico b\u1edfi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n k\u1ebfch x\u00f9. &ldquo;T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng xem b\u1ed9 phim c\u1ee7a Griezmann, nh\u01b0ng bi\u1ebft k\u1ebft th\u00fac th\u1ebf n\u00e0o&rdquo;, Costa n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Onda Cero.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Griezmann cam k\u1ebft r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Griezmann s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 n\u00fai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCosta \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T&nbsp;T\u00e2y Ban Nha tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, h\u1ecd h\u00f2a 3-3 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Atletico l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. \u0110\u00eam nay, La Roja s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Iran \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-216-boi-la-roja-van-la-ung-vien-vo-dich-421-188993.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-216-boi-la-roja-van-la-ung-vien-vo-dich.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-216-boi-la-roja-van-la-ung-vien-vo-dich-421-188993.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha (1h ng\u00e0y 21/6): B\u1edfi La Roja v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&hellip;</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Diego Costa tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/fabregas-neymar-ronaldo-hay-messi-deu-dung-sau-diego-costa-421-188722.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/fabregas-neymar-ronaldo-hay-messi-deu-dung-sau-diego-costa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/fabregas-neymar-ronaldo-hay-messi-deu-dung-sau-diego-costa-421-188722.html\">Fabregas: Neymar, Ronaldo hay Messi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee9ng sau Diego Costa</span><br>\r\n<span>Cesc Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Diego Costa, F4 tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Chelsea s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Neymar, Ronaldo hay Messi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/diego-costa-buc-xuc-khi-tbn-bi-cam-hoa-469-188614.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/diego-costa-buc-xuc-khi-tbn-bi-cam-hoa.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/diego-costa-buc-xuc-khi-tbn-bi-cam-hoa-469-188614.html\">Diego Costa b\u1ee9c x\u00fac khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</span><br>\r\n<span>Diego Costa cho r\u1eb1ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Iberia v\u1eeba qua.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3717","checkdouble":"188996"},{"date":"11:29 20/06","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/13/chu-tich-sampdoria-xac-nhan-ban-sao-khung-cho-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lucas Torreira th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, Massimo Ferrero x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal nh\u1eafm Lucas Torreira thay Wilshere</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal-172-188988.html\" target=\"_blank\">Jack Wilshere x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Arsenal</span> \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Torreira la mot chien binh dich thuc\" title=\"Lucas Torreira l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn binh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Arsenal-chieu-mo-Torreira-Tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lucas Torreira l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sampdoria v\u1edbi 36 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Lucas Torreira, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Arsenal nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lucas Torreira th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, Massimo Ferrero x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chieu mo Torreira voi gia 30 trieu euro\" title=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/chu-tich-sampdoria-xac-nhan-ban-sao-khung-cho-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015 t\u1eeb Pescara, kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Torreira th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Serie A&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecf ra 3 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Torreira, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n 30 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i. Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Arsenal s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian. Torreira s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng hai t\u00e2n binh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3716","checkdouble":"189024"},{"date":"20:08 19/06","title":"C\u00f3 c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t, G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \"tr\u1ecdng th\u01b0\u1edfng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/31/co-cong-voi-bong-da-viet-gdkt-jurgen-gede-sap-duoc-trong-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF \u0111ang t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to l\u1edbn m\u00e0 v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t.</h2><h2>VFF s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00ean nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng Jurgen Gede \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mang \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2016 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2017.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"GDKT Jurgen Gede nghi viec trong truong hop PCT phu trach chuyen mon Tran Quoc Tuan khong con lam viec o VFF.\" title=\"G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede ngh\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p PCT ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf VFF.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/28/lanh-dao-vff-noi-gi-ve-viec-gdkt-jurgen-gede-nghi-viec.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi quy ho\u1ea1ch <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam-c168-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span>, \u00f4ng Gede c\u0169ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u00f3, G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VFF c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c HLV c\u00e1c \u0110TQG Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, VFF \u0111ang th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6/2018. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd L\u00ea Ho\u00e0i Anh&nbsp;cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: &ldquo;N\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Jurgen Gede \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng, chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 do G\u0110KT Gede, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edfng. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0ng VFF s\u1ebd trao \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1ec1 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Gede tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi HLV. V\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia 61 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1eebng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 trong vai tr\u00f2 G\u0110KT, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng ho\u1eb7c HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i Iran v\u00e0 Uzbekistan.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/gdkt-jurgen-gede-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam-va-thai-lan-168-182947.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/31/gdkt-jurgen-gede-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam-va-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/gdkt-jurgen-gede-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam-va-thai-lan-168-182947.html\">G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u0103m nay, G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-de-cao-vai-tro-cua-gdkt-jurgen-gede-168-178986.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/19/thay-park-de-cao-vai-tro-cua-gdkt-nguoi-duc-trong-thanh-cong-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-de-cao-vai-tro-cua-gdkt-jurgen-gede-168-178986.html\">Th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u1ec1 cao vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a G\u0110KT ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c trong th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede trong chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u1ee7a U23...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3715","checkdouble":"188950"},{"date":"18:37 19/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 19/6: M.U t\u00ednh chi c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eadm v\u1edbi sao Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-196-mu-tinh-chi-cuc-dam-voi-sao-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U t\u00ednh ch\u01a1i \u2018t\u1ea5t tay\u2019 v\u1edbi sao Real, PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn v\u00ec Ronaldo, Unai Emery ch\u1ec9 ra 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m t\u1ea1i Arsenal, l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 19/6.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U t\u00ednh ch\u01a1i \u2018t\u1ea5t tay\u2019 v\u1edbi sao Real<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Diario Gol (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) \u0111\u01b0a tin, CLB M.U v\u1eeba b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Marco Asensio. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eebng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi Real nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 r\u00fat lui b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ra gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao. Don Balon cho bi\u1ebft sau khi M.U r\u00fat, Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua Asensio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 132 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng b\u1ecb Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u2018t\u1ea5t tay\u2019 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao Real. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 tham v\u1ecdng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Horacio Gaggioli c\u1ee7a Asensio c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn t\u1edbi Los Blancos.\u00a0<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 196 MU t\u00ednh ch\u01a1i \u2018t\u1ea5t tay\u2019 v\u1edbi sao Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 196 MU t\u00ednh ch\u01a1i \u2018t\u1ea5t tay\u2019 v\u1edbi sao Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-196-MU-tinh-choi-\u2018tat-tay\u2019-voi-sao-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 19/6:</em>\u00a0<em>M.U t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Marco Asensio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn v\u00ec Ronaldo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd SportMediaset m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, CLB PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 300 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C.Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, CLB nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 45 tri\u1ec7u euro/n\u0103m (cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi) cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. N\u1ebfu ngu\u1ed3n tin n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n ti\u1ec1n mua Neymar t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh PSG.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unai Emery ch\u1ec9 ra 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m t\u1ea1i Arsenal<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Hector Bellerin, t\u00e2n HLV Emery s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m Alexandre Lacazette, Granit Xhaka, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Hector Bellerin.<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Alexandre Lacazette m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eddi cho b\u1ed9 ba k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 Darmian<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Italy Alfredo Pedulla m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft Juventus v\u00e0 M.U v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Darmian. Juve ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed3ng l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u0111a 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, con s\u1ed1 M.U mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 15,7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Cancelo c\u1ee7a Valencia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Mexico<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf S\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, Liverpool r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hirving Lozano. Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai ng\u00f4i sao v\u00ec Conte<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Times, CLB Chelsea \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri. S\u1edf d\u0129 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00ec The Blues v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c ai s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh CLB Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli, Maurizio Sarri. Tuy nhi\u00ean cho t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U t\u00ecm nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi cho Martial<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Independent (Anh), M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 cho tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Martial. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Premier League nh\u01b0 Chelsea hay Tottenham, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ra gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c CLB ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City trao h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m cho Jorginho<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tin t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e0i Radio Kiss Kiss, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Jorginho, Joao Santos ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng Man City \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m cho th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Jorginho \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a CLB Napoli (\u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Man City) \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Man City. Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, Man City ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 47 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng 6 tri\u1ec7u euro ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed, g\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u 55 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Napoli.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3714","checkdouble":"188948"},{"date":"02:49 20/06","title":"CLB Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai trong h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Arsenal m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 hai trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Bernd Leno \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen.</h2><h2>CLB Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, trang ch\u1ee7 Arsenal.com c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, Bernd Leno. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ra s\u00e2n h\u01a1n 230 l\u1ea7n cho Bayer Leverkusen k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y n\u0103m 2011, Bernd Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Champions League trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Bayer Leverkusen v\u00e0 Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u0103m 2011. L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 Leno m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i 193 ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Arsenal thong bao chieu mo thanh cong thu thanh Bernd Leno\" title=\"CLB Arsenal th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><i>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG, Bernd Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Joachim Low tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2015 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Die Mannschaft. T\u1ea1i Confederations Cup 2017, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng tham d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0y, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eadt vinh h\u1ea1nh khi Bernd Leno gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Leverkusen \u1edf Bundesliga su\u1ed1t 7 n\u0103m qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Bernd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Arsenal v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng anh \u1ea5y trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal </span>\u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y, Petr Cech nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi m\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh CH S\u00e9c n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 36 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018-172-188928.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018-172-188928.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-172-188530.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-172-188530.html\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nArsenal mua David Luiz nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Chelsea v\u1eeba t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/premier-league-chinh-thuc-cong-bo-lich-thi-dau-mua-giai-201819-172-188479.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/premier-league-chinh-thuc-cong-bo-lich-thi-dau-mua-giai-201819.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/premier-league-chinh-thuc-cong-bo-lich-thi-dau-mua-giai-201819-172-188479.html\">Premier League ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</span><br>\r\nBan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c Premier League \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Arsenal c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 vui c\u01b0\u1eddi cho n\u1ed5i khi ph\u1ea3i m\u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3713","checkdouble":"188980"},{"date":"04:52 20/06","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jack Wilshere x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau 17 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh London.</h2><h2>Wilshere t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n t\u00e1n xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Wenger th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng Wilshere s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Arsenal. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi Wilshere s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Arsenal. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn cho Wilshere kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Ph\u00eda Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Wilshere h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2m th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Wilshere</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd x\u1ea3y ra sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p gi\u1eefa Wilshere v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-unai-emery-tro-thanh-tan-hlv-cua-arsenal-172-186893.html\" target=\"_blank\">t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery</span> g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal sau khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau nhi\u1ec1u bu\u1ed5i th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c \u1edf CLB v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0 gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a tin, t\u00f4i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u00dd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i sau nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 17 n\u0103m v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a CLB trong m\u00ecnh. Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c minh ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng sau bu\u1ed5i g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o l\u00e0 d\u00f9 c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u0169ng v\u1eabn s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t. V\u00e0 sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Emery, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf Arsenal s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 NHM \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng HLV Emery v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac \u00f4ng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 Arsenal nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-172-188980.html\">CLB Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai trong h\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-wilshere-neu-roi-arsenal-172-188936.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Wilshere n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3712","checkdouble":"188988"},{"date":"17:24 19/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua \u201cPogba Serbia\u201d?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/9/day-doi-bong-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-pogba-serbia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. T\u1edd Tuttosport tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Milinkovic-Savic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Lazio. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Hernan-Crespo-phat-bieu-ve-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU t\u1eeb b\u1ecf theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ghi t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 Europa League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. MU l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t, Mourinho nh\u1eafm Savic nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Carrick.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-milinkovicsavic-len-100-trieu-bang-172-186876.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU h\u1ecfi mua Milinkovic-Savic</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Lazio li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Man \u0111\u1ecf ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Milinkovic-Savic?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. T\u1edd Tuttosport tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/16/Igli-Tare-phat-bieu-ve-Milinkovic-Savic-va-su-that-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, BL\u0110 Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Massimiliano Allegri mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Lazio, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lazio nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 khi Milinkovic-Savic tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Juventus. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Serie A, anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3711","checkdouble":"188943"},{"date":"15:05 19/06","title":"M\u1edbi t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 v\u00ec ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/tang-tien-bi-phat-nang-vi-tiep-tuc-choi-tho-bao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018, T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u1ea1p th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0ng Ewonde (\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng). C\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Ewonde n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 r\u00fat th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/tang-tien-bi-phat-nang-vi-tiep-tuc-choi-tho-bao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u0103ng do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i cho h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL s\u1ebd b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo \"do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ewonde Epassi Louis Christian\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng HAGL, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng (\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng) c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span></span> khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ecdc theo nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f3i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a V-League. HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL gi\u1edd c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u01a1i \"r\u1eafn\" h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-duc-len-tieng-ve-quyet-dinh-treo-gio-tang-tien-168-183657.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eebng b\u1ecb b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea5m</span></span> h\u1ebft giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00ec pha b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Duy M\u1ea1nh. M\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i \"ng\u1ef1a quen \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169\". Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a HAGL l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00ec c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, HAGL to\u00e0n thua khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 9 trong BXH V-League 2018. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, HAGL s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o 17h00 (22/6).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-291-183608.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-291-183608.html\">\u0102n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t C\u1ef0C N\u1eb6NG</span><br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 n\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3710","checkdouble":"188924"},{"date":"15:14 19/06","title":"V\u00ec Conte Chelsea ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi 2 sao kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/vi-conte-chelsea-chua-the-ky-hop-dong-voi-2-sao-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri v\u00ec t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lewandowski v\u00e0 Michael Seri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec Conte</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song vi\u1ec7c ch\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao kh\u1ee7ng v\u00ec Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao kh\u1ee7ng v\u00ec Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/vi-conte-chelsea-chua-the-ky-hop-dong-voi-2-sao-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u00ec Conte, Chelsea ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Times, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 nh\u1eafm b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri. Tuy nhi\u00ean, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJean Michael Seri mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge, song vi\u1ec7c Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c ai s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y lo l\u1eafng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a The Blues kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Napoli.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Chelsea, song v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c The The Blues v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef hay sa th\u1ea3i Conte khi\u1ebfn Lewandowski c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t an, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real thay v\u00ec c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli, Maurizio Sarri. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/ms.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maurizio Sarri nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1ebd nh\u00f3m h\u1ecdp v\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, The Blues ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Conte.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m, Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i Lewandowski v\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-mua-trung-ve-koulibaly-cua-napoli-172-182256.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Koulibaly c\u1ee7a Napoli</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi t\u1eeb 120 \u0111\u1ebfn 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3709","checkdouble":"188922"},{"date":"15:50 19/06","title":"Unai Emery ch\u1ec9 t\u00ean 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/unai-emery-chi-ten-5-cai-ten-khong-the-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Hector Bellerin, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m Alexandre Lacazette, Granit Xhaka, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Hector Bellerin.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng, c\u1ef1u HLV PSG mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal 2018 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal 2018 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/Chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-2018-khong-ban-5-cai-ten-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Emery mu\u1ed1n Aubameyang v\u00e0 Lacazette kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Hector Bellerin, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m Alexandre Lacazette, Granit Xhaka, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Hector Bellerin.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Alexandre Lacazette m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eddi cho b\u1ed9 ba k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGranit Xhaka m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates. Hector Bellerin c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u1ea3 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ec1u cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Arsenal, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Emery mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 3 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng HLV Unai Emery c\u0169ng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN s\u1ebd c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery lam HLV Arsenal\" title=\"Emery lam HLV Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/unai-emery-chi-ten-5-cai-ten-khong-the-roi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Emery mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea2Arsenal 2018 mua 3 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner t\u1eeb Juventus theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7&nbsp; m\u00f4n Bernd Leno v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Torreira.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018-172-188928.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018-172-188928.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Petr Cech.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean Emery c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-sap-mua-duoc-sokratis-172-187253.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis c\u1ee7a Dortmund</span>, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3708","checkdouble":"188927"},{"date":"16:10 19/06","title":"Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hirving Lozano \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Mexico b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap Mexico \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Liverpool-muon-mua-Hirving-Lozano-cua-PSV-Eindhoven-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lozano gi\u00fap \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 1-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hirving Lozano l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t cho Mexico, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0o g\u00f3c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2018, Hirving Lozano c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSV Eindhoven. \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 19 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 tung ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 11 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSV Eindhoven. S\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1ea7n Lozano c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lozano</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lozano ghi ban mo ti so trong tran dau giua Duc vs Mexico.\" title=\"Lozano ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Tin-nong-World-Cup-2018-ngay-186-Anh-manh,-nhung-van-kem-Bi-hinh-anh-4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lozano</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/lyon-chinh-thuc-xac-minh-thuc-hu-vu-liverpool-mua-fekir-172-188158.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool kh\u00f3 mua Nabil Fekir</span> h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Hirving Lozano nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Hirving Lozano, HLV Unai Emery c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i. Ngo\u00e0i Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal th\u00ec MU v\u00e0 Everton c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hirving Lozano.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo-172-188935.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo-172-188935.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u01a1\u1eddi Anh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPSV Eindhoven m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Lozano, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi PSV, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Lozano cho ph\u00e9p c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3707","checkdouble":"188928"},{"date":"16:37 19/06","title":"Liverpool ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u01a1\u1eddi Anh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea9y Daniel Sturridge kh\u1ecfi Anfield</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Daniel Sturridge g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/26/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Sturridge</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRoberto Firmino l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed HLV Klopp c\u00f2n \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Dominic Solanke h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. Ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Sturridge \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi West Brom theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/klopp-buong-loi-cay-dang-voi-sturridge-172-178858.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge</span> \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Sturridge</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd The Telegraph, West Brom mu\u1ed1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Sturridge, song vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho West Brom.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/21/Liverpool-giam-gia-ban-tien-dao-Daniel-Sturridge-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Sturridge</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Sevilla v\u00e0 Fenerbahce. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 Sturridge v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t t\u00e2n binh Wolvehampton l\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sturridge. Vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan ng\u1ea1i khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Wolvehampton \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Sturridge m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi Sturridge c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3706","checkdouble":"188935"}]}